<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbe054461-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s7381e"><num value="7381e">§ 7381e.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Out of funds authorized to be appropriated for the Office of Science of the Department of Energy in a fiscal year, there are authorized to be appropriated to the Secretary for carrying out university research support and other science, mathematics, and engineering education programs authorized by this part and administered by the Office of Science of the Department of Energy, $40,000,000 for each of fiscal years 2023 through 2027.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idbe054462-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/101/510/dC/tXXXI/s3169">Pub. L. 101–510, div. C, title XXXI, § 3169</ref>, formerly § 3168, <date date="1990-11-05">Nov. 5, 1990</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/104/1843">104 Stat. 1843</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/105/245/tIII/s309/b/2/D">Pub. L. 105–245, title III, § 309(b)(2)(D)</ref>, <date date="1998-10-07">Oct. 7, 1998</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/112/1853">112 Stat. 1853</ref>; renumbered § 3169, <ref href="/us/pl/109/58/tXI/s1105/b/1">Pub. L. 109–58, title XI, § 1105(b)(1)</ref>, <date date="2005-08-08">Aug. 8, 2005</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/119/939">119 Stat. 939</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/110/69/tV/s5003/d/2">Pub. L. 110–69, title V, § 5003(d)(2)</ref>, <date date="2007-08-09">Aug. 9, 2007</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/121/603">121 Stat. 603</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/117/167/dB/tI/s10111/b">Pub. L. 117–167, div. B, title I, § 10111(b)</ref>, <date date="2022-08-09">Aug. 9, 2022</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/136/1456">136 Stat. 1456</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
